    "notes":  "## v0.2.0 - Boards, Dev Tools \u0026 themes\n\n**New**\n- Kanban boards with drag-and-drop lists and cards, progress header, and board colors\n- Card detail panel with priorities, due dates, tags, and completion\n- Dev Tools panel with live web preview and GitHub activity per workspace\n- GitHub integration via GitHub CLI (PRs, issues, CI, commits)\n- Appearance themes (Dracula, Catppuccin, Nord, One Dark, Tokyo Night, and more)\n- Integrations settings section\n\n**Changed**\n- Sidebar split into Workspaces and Boards\n- Settings reorganized into Keyboard, Terminal, Appearance, Integrations, and System\n- Terminal portal roots and split-pane snap for stabler layouts\n\n**Fixed**\n- Terminal resize when Dev Tools panel opens or resizes\n- Empty workspace and board redirects after deleting the last item",
